/*ðŸ’¼ Question  Find the Index of the Largest Element
ðŸ§© Question:
Write a SystemVerilog function that:

Takes an integer dynamic array as input.

Returns the index of the largest element in the array.

ðŸ§  Requirements:
Use a function (not a task).

Use ref for the array argument.

Use a for loop and comparison logic.

Return the index (not the value).*/



module tb;
int a[]='{2,4,45,68,9};
int index;
function automatic void largest_index(ref int p[],output int y);
int idx;
int dx=p[0];
for(int i=1;i<p.size();i++)
begin
if(p[i]>dx)
begin
dx=p[i];
idx=i;
end
end
y=idx;
endfunction
initial
begin
largest_index(a,index);
$display("index of largest element:%d",index);
end
endmodule

output:index of largest element:          3
